+CG_HUDEdgeShift
+
+Widescreen HUD edge anchoring. On a framebuffer wider than 4:3, r_aspectCorrect2D
+pillarboxes the 2D layer, which rides the corner HUD widgets inboard with the
+pillarbox band. Return the number of 640-space virtual pixels to shift each side
